    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Tip: If using an air fryer, preheat the <strong>air fryer</strong> to 160\u00b0C/180\u00b0C</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Higgidy chicken & leek pie[s] </strong>to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If using an air fryer bake at 160\u00b0C for 15-20 mins!</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the pie is cooking, peel your <strong>potatoes </strong>and chop them into large, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped potatoes </strong>to a pot with plenty of<strong> boiled water </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Return the<strong> cooked potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mash until smooth</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them to refresh them</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-chicken-and-leek-pie-with-mash-and-peas/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Higgidy chicken & leek pie[s] </strong>with the<strong> mash </strong>and<strong> peas </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
